The paper discusses recent advances in computer vision using deep learning with RGB imagery and introduces an improved self-taught feature learning framework for HSI and MSI data. The paper also discusses a semi-supervised classification algorithm. These topics are closely related to computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), and multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
